posting_body: ['The View & You!', 'Ascending seaplanes.', 'City lights.', 'Space Needle sunsets.', 'Helm is a boutique tower in South Lake Union with inspiring, unobstructed Lake Union views.', "Perched atop Google's new campus, Helm is a modern skyward escape at the edge of it all.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 91', 'OR Text', '91', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom + 1 Den, 1 Bath, approximately 906 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Decks*', '- Solar Shades', '- Ample Storage + Walk-in Closets', '- Central Air Conditioning', '- Luxury hardwood style floors', '- Virtual Tour of Our Homes: https://youtu.be/tUKnO7P6AOw', '- Unobstructed views of Lake Union*', '- City + Space Needle Views*', '- Energy Star Whirlpool Washer and Dryer', '- Polished Quartz countertops and backsplashes', '- KitchenAid Stainless Steel Appliances', '*in select apartments', 'Community Amenities', '- Dog Relief/Run Area', '- Views Of Lake Union Like No Other', '- Board/Meeting Room', '- Bike Storage', '- Rooftop Lounge/Club Room', '- Rooftop Deck', '- Outdoor Fire Pit', '- Sun Deck', '- Billiards and Shuffleboard Area', '- Outdoor Kitchen', '- Package Concierge', '- Pet Relief Area', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $300 deposit per pet (refundable).', 'Pet rent is $50.', 'Please contact our leasing office for more information about our Pet Policy.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Helm', '602 Terry Ave N, Seattle, WA, 98109', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'fXDzi26QY4h']
